Author: BlockFood
Title: 🚀[BOUNTY] BlockFood- Give the sharing economy back to the people
Body: Hey! We're going to take a step back since we didn't complete our pre-sale as expected. More communication to come

Author: BlockFood
Title: 🚀[BOUNTY] BlockFood- Give the sharing economy back to the people
Body: Dear bounty campaign participants,  First of all a huge THANK YOU to all of you who helped us get our word out there on Twitter, joined our community on Telegram and/or displayed our signature.  Unfortunately, our initial plan is now officially delayed. Indeed we were not able to complete the pre-sale due to insufficient funds. We're not dead! We have a contingency plan and we are going to communicate about it very soon.  Meanwhile, rest assured ; bounty participants will be rewarded with tokens sooner or later. But in order for these tokens to have value, we obviously need to reach a successful token sale!  So we're going to communicate with you during the next month, to enroll you in our new plan. Give us some time though, we didn't plan for this to happen!  Thanks again to all participants   Some full transparency to come in our blog about what happened.

Body: WEBSITE - WHITE PAPER - GITHUB - MEDIUM - TWITTER - TELEGRAM  BlockFood  Give the sharing economy back to the people    Welcome to the BlockFood bounty campaign  We have reserved up to 5% of the BlockFoodTokens for this bounty program and we hope to get you on board with the BlockFood adventure.  Given the mechanism behind BlockFood's token sale, this amount can vary from: - The minimum total supply of BFT is: 14 285 710 BFT - The maximum total supply of BFT is: 925 714 280 BFT  The minimum amount we will distribute is: 714 280 BFT The maximum amount we will distribute is: 46 285 710 BFT  The total of BFT we are going to give to bounty hunters is distributed on 10 000 points. If you get 10 000 points, you get the whole pie. If you get 100 points, you get 1% of the amount of BFT we will distribute. The value of a point depends of the success of the project. The more the token sale is successful, the more BFT you will get.  Here is a recap of the value of a point depending on the final token sale result:  Token sale result (Eth) 1 000 5 000 10 000 15 000 25 000 40 000 54 000 Estimated BFT Supply 14 285 710 85 714 290 171 428 570 257 142 860 428 571 430 685 714 290 925 714 290 Distributed 714 290 4 285 710 8 571 430 12 857 140 21 428 570 34 285 710 46 285 710 1 points (BFT) 71 429 857 1 286 2 143 3 429 4 629 10 points 714 4 286 8 571 12 857 21 429 34 286 46 286 50 points 3 571 21 429 42 857 64 286 107 143 171 429 231 429 100 points 7 143 42 857 85 714 128 571 214 286 342 857 462 857  If the token sale is successful, participants will receive BFT with the following formula : Code: BOUNTY = (POINTS / TOTAL OF POINTS) * TOTAL_SUPPLY * 5%  Pre-sale campaigns  2000 points are dedicated to the pre-sale.  We are looking for help on three subjects: Twitter Signatures Telegram  The campaign starts now and ends on the February 8th 2018.  Twitter campaign / Target reached - 500 points  Conditions for applying to the twitter campaign: Have 200 followers  Activity required for a participation to be considered complete: Follow @BlockFood Retweet all tweets from the BlockFood twitter account  Bounty: 20 points  Register here: no more spot on this bounty.  Telegram campaign - 500 points  Conditions for applying to the telegram campaign: Join the Telegram group https://t.me/blockfood Stay in Telegram group until end of campaign Reply to this thread "joined telegram campaign"  Register here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdDBZrYZDHfIzIOgQ22bVBP5lBr8NZ7Ag7T-UqEGXXOyLTBUg/viewform?usp=sf_link  Bounty: 2 points  Signature campaign - 500 points  Conditions for applying to the signature campaign: Be at least a Jr. Member Post at least 5 messages per week on average  Activity required for a participation to be considered complete: Use the signature for the whole campaign  Your activity is automatically checked by a bot: https://github.com/BlockFood/bitcointalk-signature-checker  Signatures:  Jr. Member: Example:  BlockFood - PRE-SALE IS LIVE  Code: Code: [center][b][url=http://blockfood.io]BlockFood[/url][/b] - [url=http://blockfood.io/pre-sale]PRE-SALE IS LIVE[/url][/center]   Member:  Example: BlockFood - Give the sharing economy back to the people - 2018/1/8 → 2018/2/8 | PRE-SALE IS LIVE  Code: Code: [center][b][url=https://blockfood.io]BlockFood[/url][/b] - Give the sharing economy back to the people - [b][url=https://blockfood.io/pre-sale]2018/1/8 → 2018/2/8 | PRE-SALE IS LIVE[/url][/b][/center]   Full:  Example: BlockFood - Give the sharing economy back to the people - 2018/1/8 → 2018/2/8 | PRE-SALE IS LIVE  Code: Code: [center][b][url=https://blockfood.io][color=#4B3F80]BlockFood[/color][/url][/b] - Give the sharing economy back to the people - [b][url=https://blockfood.io/pre-sale][color=#4B3F80]2018/1/8 → 2018/2/8 | PRE-SALE IS LIVE[/color][/url][/b][/center]  Sr. Member and above:  A huge THANK YOU to Dayx for this awesome work: Visit his page on https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2703739.0 He got 100 points for helping us out on his own and provide us this signature. For your participation to be considered complete, you have to wear our signature for the whole time on the pre-sale campaign.

Author: BlockFood
Title: 🚀[BOUNTY] BlockFood- Give the sharing economy back to the people
Body: The twitter campaign participation will be automatically checked using an inhouse-tool. It will look back in each users history to see if they have done the task: Retweet all tweets from the BlockFood twitter account. This check will happen at the end of the pre-sale campaign (February 8th 2018).  The twitter campaign makes your earn 2 points. Those two points represent 0.2% of the whole bounty campaign. The value of those 2 points in BFT will depend on the scale of the success of the token-sale.  Here is a recap for the value of Twitter campaign participation in BFT:  Token sale result (Eth) 1 000 5 000 10 000 15 000 25 000 40 000 54 000 Value of a twitter campaign participation (2 points) (in BFT) 142 858 1714 2 572 4 286 6 858 9 258  The final value of your participation depends on the scale of the success of the token-sale. If we succeed, your participation can be very lucrative. That's a win-win situation

Author: Jordanuttos
Title: 🚀[BOUNTY] BlockFood- Give the sharing economy back to the people
Body: BlockFood, does the reward depend on the number of Twitter subscribers? How much $ in 1 BFT?

Author: BlockFood
Title: 🚀[BOUNTY] BlockFood- Give the sharing economy back to the people
Body: As long as you meet the number of followers required to join the campaign, you get 20 points. There is no correlation between the number of followers and the bounty.  For the price of 1 BFT, we cannot give you an exact value, as it depends on the current price of Ethereum. Nevertheless, here is an estimation:  Code: 1000 BFT ~= 1 Eth ~= (at current rate) 724 $ 1 BFT ~= 0,724 $  Which gives, for the twitter campaign : Code: (amount raised in Eth) bounty value ~= $ (1 000) 142 BFT ~= 102 $ (5 000) 858 BFT ~= 621 $ (10 000) 1714 BFT ~= 1 240 $ (15 000) 2 572 BFT ~= 1 862 $ (25 000) 4 286 BFT ~= 3 103 $ (40 000) 6 858 BFT ~= 4 965 $ (54 000) 9 258 BFT ~= 6 702 $  The numbers are an approximation as we have no control over the price of Ethereum.
